OL,3,CBurnham on track to become next PM as
OL,4,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back him
OL,6,FThe former Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fsaid on Thursday evening that he is
OL,8,F"deeply grateful" for the support.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,F"As the first day of nominations draws
OL,16,Fto a close, I am deeply grateful to
OL,17,Fthe 322 Labour MPs who have put their
OL,18,Ftrust in me and nominated me for
OL,19,Fleader of the Labour Party," he wrote
OL,20,Fon X.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@QO]wD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
