PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783689573
OL,3,CBurnham on track to become next PM as
OL,4,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back him
OL,6,F"Their support comes from across the
OL,7,FPLP and reflects a shared belief that
OL,8,FBritain needs a new approach to
OL,9,Fpolitics. That is the circuit breaker
OL,10,FI am offering: power out of
OL,11,FWestminster, an economy rewired for
OL,12,Fordinary people, and good growth in
OL,13,Fevery postcode.
OL,15,F"I want to empower MPs to bring the
OL,16,Fexperiences of their constituents into
OL,17,Fthe heart of government and harness
OL,18,Fthe full breadth of our Labour
OL,19,Fmovement, drawing on all its
OL,20,Ftraditions and beliefs in pursuit of a
OL,21,Fcommon purpose.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
