PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783689573
OL,3,CBurnham on track to become next PM as
OL,4,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back him
OL,6,F"I want to thank every colleague who
OL,7,Fhas nominated me for their commitment
OL,8,Fto that vision."
OL,10,FThe Housing Secretary, Steve Reed, was
OL,11,Fone of only four Cabinet members who
OL,12,Fdid not nominate Mr Burnham on
OL,13,FThursday, alongside Home Secretary
OL,14,FShabana Mahmood and Energy Secretary
OL,15,FEd Miliband, as well as party
OL,16,Fchairwoman Anna Turley.
OL,18,FBoth Miliband and Mahmood have been
OL,19,Fmentioned as potential chancellors.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
