CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783689573
OL,3,CBurnham on track to become next PM as
OL,4,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back him
OL,6,FThe lack of nomination does not
OL,7,Fnecessarily mean the four cabinet
OL,8,Fmembers do not support Mr Burnham, as
OL,9,Fnominations must be made in person or
OL,10,Fthrough a limited number of proxy
OL,11,Fvotes.
OL,13,FAs nominations opened on Thursday,
OL,14,FStarmer told reporters he thought Mr
OL,15,FBurnham would make a good prime
OL,16,Fminister, saying they had known each
OL,17,Fother "a long time".
OL,26,@yD@GOUyD@SO]
